cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with using deep learning techniques to enhance the resolution of SEM images. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) also suggests that the paper could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves image processing and analysis, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
